    <item>
      <title>特朗普的快速贸易行动扰乱市场，油价波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者对特朗普政府迅速采取的贸易举措作出反应，油价出现波动，美国先是威胁对哥伦比亚实施一系列限制措施，随后又推迟了这一决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 23:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DeepSeek 助力中国人工智能发展，亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市上涨，部分原因是对中国人工智能的乐观情绪，不受唐纳德特朗普对哥伦比亚征收关税导致其他地区风险偏好降低的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/asia-eyes-cautious-open-as-tariffs-remain-in-focus-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 22:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对哥伦比亚征收关税，美元本周开局不利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/dollar-starts-week-on-front-foot-after-trump-s-colombia-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国对哥伦比亚征收关税的短暂威胁表明贸易风险仍然笼罩着货币市场之后，美元本周开盘小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/dollar-starts-week-on-front-foot-after-trump-s-colombia-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 21:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>货币波动将消灭新兴市场套利交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/currency-volatility-set-to-wipe-out-emerging-market-carry-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普政府的关税威胁和美元进一步上涨的前景挤压了回报，新兴市场投资者对套利交易变得越来越谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/currency-volatility-set-to-wipe-out-emerging-market-carry-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度塔塔汽车和玛鲁蒂铃木因节日需求和折扣而获得喘息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/india-s-tata-motors-maruti-suzuki-get-respite-on-festival-demand-discounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度经济低迷的背景下，巴贾杰汽车有限公司 (Bajaj Auto Ltd.)、塔塔汽车有限公司 (Tata Motors Ltd.) 和玛鲁蒂铃木印度有限公司 (Maruti Suzuki India Ltd.) 应该在上个季度的节日期间获得一些支撑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/india-s-tata-motors-maruti-suzuki-get-respite-on-festival-demand-discounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 01:35:45 GMT</pubDate>
